.DT
set_newline_mode
Disk World creator help
set_newline_mode

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_newline_mode -  This method sets the 'newline' mode for room description extras.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_newline_mode(int mode)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^mode%^RESET%^ - the new mode.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the 'newline' mode for room description extras.
If set to 1, a newline will be inserted after all feature and
neighbouring room items. 1 is the default.
.EP

